          <p>
            • Achieve a FIDE rating of 2300 or higher.<br>
            • Earn three WGM norms in international competition.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-segment">
          <h4>WIM (Woman International Master)</h4>
          <p>
            • Achieve a FIDE rating of 2200 or higher.<br>
            • Earn three WIM norms in international competition.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-segment">
          <h4>WFM (Woman FIDE Master)</h4>
          <p>
            • Achieve a FIDE rating of 2100 or higher.<br>
            • No norms are required.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-segment">
          <h4>WCM (Woman Candidate Master)</h4>
          <p>
            • Achieve a FIDE rating of 2000 or higher.<br>
            • No norms are required.
          </p>
        </div>
